Class DefaultCapacityBundle

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CapacityBundle, StructureInstance

    public class DefaultCapacityBundle
extends Object
implements CapacityBundle, StructureInstance
    A simple collection of capacity originators, all with the same base capacity type; i.e., CONSUMPTION or PRODUCTION.
    Author:
    Prashant Reddy, John Collins
